{"type": "article", "id": 62019, "title": "耐克发布法国女足世界杯球衣，以及，2019 秋冬这些包款正流行 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-03-13T07:04:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2447, "name": "手袋"}, {"id": 21598, "name": "特步"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 3113, "name": "Salvatore Ferragamo"}, {"id": 57242, "name": "Phillip Lim"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190313150146ZInbDdF8KeA43SVh.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1627810216615043098&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc\" rel=\"nofollow\">特步去年净利润增长 61%</a> </strong>| 特步于 3 月 12 日发布了 2018 年财报。财报显示，该公司全年营收达 63.83 亿元，创历史新高，收入增加 25%；经营利润达到 10.44 亿元；净利润增加 61%。从更为详细的一些数据来看，特步零售网络的门店销售额呈现中双位数增长；电商收入占比超过 20%；毛利率达到 44.3％，创上市以来新高；特步儿童营收增长超过 50%。</p><p>财务总监何睿博在财报后的会议上表示，过去三年特步品牌定位从“时尚运动”转为运动品牌，专注跑步市场，并由批发转为零售。这些措施初见成效。该公司计划下一步推进多品牌战略，与拥有 Wolverine 集团合作，以合资的方式将 Wolverine 旗下的跑鞋品牌 Saucony 和户外鞋品牌 Merrell 引入中国。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/salvatore-ferragamo-profitability-revenues-down-in-1203082927/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Salvatore Ferragamo 去年净利润跌幅超过 21%</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 截至去年 12 月 31 日的 2018 财年，意大利奢侈品牌 Salvatore Ferragamo 销售额同比下跌 3.3% 至 13.4 亿欧元，营业利润同比减少 19.5% 至 1.5 亿欧元，净利润下滑 21.1% 至 9000 万欧元。</p><p>从业务分类看，核心鞋履业务销售额下滑 5.9% 至 5.55 亿欧元，占总销售额的 41.2%；手袋及皮具配饰业务销售额增长 1% 至 5.21 亿欧元，占总额的 38.7%；香水业务增长 5.6% 至 9410 万欧元，占总额的 7%；而服饰业务则下跌 15% 至 7640 万欧元，占总额的 5.6%。</p><p>从区域来看，亚太区仍为其主要市场，营收占比达 37.6%。去年该区域营收下滑 1% 至 5.01 亿欧元，其中大中华区持续增长，第四季度中国大陆零售销售额增幅同比增长 7.6%；而东南亚区则表现不佳。欧洲、中东和非洲销售额下滑 6.1% 至 3.30 亿欧元，营收占比为 24.5%。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/financial/moschino-alberta-ferretti-parent-aeffe-sees-2018-profits-gain-1203082625/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moschino 母公司去年净利润增长 46%</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Moschino 母公司 Aeffe 周二发布的 2018 财年业绩报告显示，去年该集团销售额增长 10.9% 至 3.47 亿欧元，净利润增长 46% 至 1670 万欧元。从业务分类来看，成衣部门销售额增长 10.8% 至 2.66 亿欧元，鞋履及皮具部门增长 9.3% 至 1.18 亿欧元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.prosoccerusa.com/mls/nike-unveils-14-kits-ahead-of-2019-fifa-womens-world-cup/#gallery/debe26d17c7bce0427b23712f58671e2/17405\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>3 月 12 日，耐克与来自世界各国的 40 名女性运动员在巴黎共同发布了今夏法国女足世界杯的 14 套国家队队服</strong>。</a><br></p><p>此外，耐克还宣布与欧足联女足达成为期三年的合作协议。在此协议下，耐克将成为欧足联女子比赛用球供应商，并支持欧洲足球协会联盟（UEFA）为巩固足球在欧洲女子团体运动中的领先地位而制定的“团结起来，我们一起实力上场”（Together #weplaystrong） 计划。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131414282kdncxRHaCA6rYqK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498929\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>智利</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141606idFltT49uDo0jsJ5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498929\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>巴西</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141843hcPdyx4eT1I0vJ6E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498929\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>新西兰</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141725Kfnh3oDqmcJPVuYs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.492537\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>中国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141715ZNdSuMDOrRi2m0Fw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.979021\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>中国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141737YuDkBcpw26Sj3Iqd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>中国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141345zwv2GTDo5aAdb9eu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.782123\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>法国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141417PUiLuTBaACHhygYx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.738889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>美国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141520xUI4LnQqWlMbtgTa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.838323\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>澳大利亚</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141511E04QD7FpxCI619lS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>澳大利亚</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141640VvpQqySndE9a6LA0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.845411\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>加拿大</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141657kePL2EiNCr1HUmwq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>加拿大</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131417535NZMG130YQC6S8JV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.682222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>英格兰</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141804VkfCMmEJSzjl9F6i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>英格兰</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141830xy7ibWm5HC1QTRsA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>荷兰</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131419246OonaP3NGtj9q2ZK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>尼日利亚</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141940bWNqUDX5FZ2HTMPV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.768889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>挪威</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313141955caPqQ5zdHslfOkVx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>韩国</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131420156RXCrLDmxkej4KU1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>南非</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/design-living/11587/3-1-phillip-lim-viviane-sassen-collaboration-cookbook-more-than-our-bellies\" rel=\"nofollow\">华裔美籍服装设计师林能平（Phillip Lim）与摄影师&nbsp;Viviane Sassen 共同创作了一本烹饪书“<em>More Than Our Bellies”</em>（《裹腹之上》）<em>。</em></a></strong><br></p><p>摄影师 Viviane Sassen 多次为林能平的服装品牌&nbsp;3.1 Phillip Lim 拍摄广告大片。两人之前策划了一系列以“going home”（归乡）为主题的影像，带模特回到他们的家乡，拍摄他们与亲人及当地社区共处的场景。</p><p>这本烹饪书也是“归乡”概念的延伸。林能平在其中展示了母亲传授给他的 12 道菜谱， Viviane Sassen 则配以她创作的 20 多幅艺术作品。“一场通过美食和视觉实现的爱之旅（A journey of love through food and visuals）”，林能平<a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/design-living/11587/3-1-phillip-lim-viviane-sassen-collaboration-cookbook-more-than-our-bellies\" rel=\"nofollow\">对 <em>Another Magazine</em> 说</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121651wfp95NiIXH4A7nxQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.322751\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121651TZOnaj3IPBx8YStR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.326260\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121652F2OJjvUnhZX7mY19.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.321004\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121650Ho8asVEYdeu0wR1A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.314060\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121652q4DBECG9da1eNLZp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.315789\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121652HvQu3dltnJ7SD2bF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.310616\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121650Jrblo54A7HXcjqE1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.322751\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121650JCmvTxjDWXyt0f5c.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.764000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121651SrbAmftOcao5PpYl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.762000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313121652TMUSA0DXlOQ2mtF8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.795000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/malika-favre-new-yorker-cover-frida-kahlo-illustration-120319\" rel=\"nofollow\">伦敦插画师 Malika Favre 为《纽约客》创作了了 2019 年 3 月 18 日杂志封面。</a></strong><br></p><p>这一期《纽约客》的主要关注点是时尚议题，包括对 Louis Vuitton 艺术总监 Virgil Abloh 以及运动服饰品牌 Outdoor Voices 的采访。</p><p>为配合“春季”及“时尚”主题，Maika Favre 以墨西哥现代女画家弗里达（Frida Kahlo）五彩斑斓的衣橱和标志性形象为灵感，创作了以下封面。这也是 Malika Favre 第七次为《纽约客》创作封面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313140744MtHJyqfsSrobpjuk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.364641\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/trends/g26292155/fall-2019-bag-trends/?slide=1\" rel=\"nofollow\"><em>Harper's Bazaar</em> 总结了 2019 秋冬秀场上手袋的 6 个趋势：</a></strong><br></p><p><strong>1）软绵绵，毛绒绒：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313133642PtOSHh3vGQTACwdR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Chanel</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131337197MXL6hrka2NiQ1TH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497959\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Max Mara</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313133728o8ZKUCzXa4WdjwyO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Miu Miu</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313133828c41UfZwaQODAP9zo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Off-White</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>2）两只包叠背：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134013xnIvha08Bzqg1ikj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Fendi</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134107w8NHzd23IKSWMYmi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Off-White</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134118pUK4YGqMolP8ZXtf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Ulla Johnson</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134148AjxSTUsM2bVtRnY7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Rebecca Minkoff</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>3）奇形怪状的小手提包：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134346P5EuLA43J7CrS6Ne.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Christopher Kane</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134420fxkS7e3VRbWgusNw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Oscar de la Renta</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134532Dm4LOZ2i7rBdTSMP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497959\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Brandon Maxwell</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134559WQxoRLF6vf8sJEdN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Bottega Veneta</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134617zVgGYkfRelq05i7N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502041\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Louis Vuitton</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134647T7O2jDbXfRCGMNnF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Emilio Pucci</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134845ZQGb6nWm2k1Dxpze.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497959\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Simone Rocha</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>4）还是腰包：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313134945ksfnKTrUE8iRhwy3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.245918\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Fendi&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135004Su8AKUJnMk39oQtd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503061\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Dior</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135100d8cXJq6V0RmsrxNb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Chanel</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135032uKc2Vk35vOrWDb9z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Versace</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135048CAUcPE123R64lanw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501302\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Roberto Cavalli</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131352274TRSMpZ0V7quNbvY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Zimmermann</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>5）微型迷你包：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135408NKcJUtnBGgTkqWYE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502604\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Carolina Herrera</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135423m1WjkYzMRst29GnU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jacquemus</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135432md8Iq3JFL0eu1byC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Alexander McQueen</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135441yVdh9ibcFAkBMQpv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Givenchy</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135601sLlaf5NikURQWOV8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Brandon Maxwell</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135609eCtuwFRBXVT3ZJaq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501302\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Ferragamo</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>6）珍稀皮革花纹包：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313140104UMfaxShNJ1HrqtTG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Louis Vuitton</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131357394VjkZf3dxQoYvzEr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.243490\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Celine</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135752kq43xOZVmTcoKL7y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Lanvin</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135726hbZEgxKRInYulqDp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Max Mara</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019031313575982ZDjQkXflcKHCoA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Loewe</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong>7）超大背包：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135924kdP1CGwJ6TpDboWY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jil Sander</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313135940o0tdcLyjDrC924JQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498698\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Fendi</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190313140025IH3hfmyiUN7CL5ZF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.497396\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>off-White</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201903131400335HU2hpzMOiXV0uCD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>D